                    <span>This is one of the most enjoyable as well as one of the most informative books I have read in recent years.  This book examines the creative process as illustrated by the thinking strategies employed by creative geniuses throughout history in the sciences, arts, and industry. The book enlightened and inspired me to become a proactive thinker. The book helped me understand what creativity is and how I can be more creative in my business.
<br />
<br /></span>
                  
