                    <span>I've been looking for years for the right book that would provide practical advice that is historically founded.  This is it. Michael provides the techniques with the histories of the techniques as to how geniuses have profited from them throughout history. This is, without question, the best book on creative thinking that I have ever read. Bar none.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Paradigm</div>
                    <div>
