                    <span>Michael Michalko' companion volume to 'Thinkertoys' is highly recommended. The author hosts a guided tour through strategies and tactics designed to challenge, and ultimately enlighten us all. There are relevant examples and illustrations. There are cogent observations from the creators themselves. And there is much, much more. This book can be properly viewed as a paradigm for creative thinking.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Best book on creative thinking</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
