                    </div>
                    <span>I have read many books on creativity and creative thinking techniques. "Cracking Creativity"is not only the best book on creative thinking I have ever read it also has research that clearly explains the thinking strategies that the creative geniuses throughout history used to get their ideas. After explaining the strategy, Michalko provides practical creative thinking techniques, based on the strategy, to help you generate the ideas you need. It's fantastic. I am just reading it for the second time. I would highly recommended it to anyone who wants or needs to become more creative.</span>
                  
              
